STEP: Implement session expiration (slug: implement-session-expiration)
  SUMMARY: Add server-side session timeout logic and cover the scenarios with
    tests.
  CONTEXT:
    The session middleware currently does not track last-access time.
      This step adds that tracking and the expiration check.
  TASKS:
    [ ] Add `last_accessed_at` column to the `sessions` table
    [ ] Update session middleware to refresh `last_accessed_at` on
    each request
    [ ] @spec auth Session expiration: Idle timeout
    [ ] @spec auth Session expiration: Force logout on password change
